瑟斯顿摩尔分享了令人着迷的悲剧新歌“The Diver” https://www.nme.com/news/music/thurston-moore-shares-captivatingly-tragic-new-song-the-diver-3787373?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=thurston-moore-shares-captivatingly-tragic-新歌潜水员Anagricel DuranMon, 26 Aug 2024 14:12:34 +0000 Music NewsNewsRockhttps://www.nme.com/?p=3787373 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Thurston-moore-performing.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="瑟斯顿·摩尔 (Thurston Moore) 于 2023 年 7 月 24 日在爱尔兰都柏林的 Whelan’s 演出。 （基兰·弗罗斯特/雷德芬斯摄）" decoding="async" fetchpriority="high" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Thurston-moore-performing.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Thurston-moore-performing-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Thurston-moore-performing-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Thurston-moore-performing-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Thurston-moore-performing-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Thurston-moore-performing-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>这首歌是他的专辑“Flow Critical Lucidity”中最新发行的歌曲</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/thurston-moore-shares-captivatingly-tragic-new-song-the-diver-3787373">瑟斯顿·摩尔 (Thurston Moore) 分享的令人着迷的悲剧新歌《The Diver》的</a>帖子首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Thurston-moore-performing.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="瑟斯顿·摩尔 (Thurston Moore) 于 2023 年 7 月 24 日在爱尔兰都柏林的 Whelan’s 演出。 （基兰·弗罗斯特/雷德芬斯摄）" decoding="async" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Thurston-moore-performing.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Thurston-moore-performing-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Thurston-moore-performing-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Thurston-moore-performing-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Thurston-moore-performing-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Thurston-moore-performing-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="/artists/Thurston-Moore">瑟斯顿摩尔</a>分享了他即将发行的专辑中令人着迷的悲剧新单曲“The Diver”。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多：</strong> <strong><a href="https://www.nme.com/features/music-interviews/thurston-moore-by-the-fire-madonna-oasis-keanu-reeves-2781763">摇滚乐会杀死脑细胞吗？！ ——瑟斯顿·摩尔</a></strong></li></ul><p>最新单曲的歌词由 Radieux Radio 创作，描述了一名潜水员最终死于野生动物的生活。贝斯手 Deb Googe（ <a href="/artists/My-Bloody-Valentine">My Bloody Valentine</a> ）和打击乐手 Jem Doulton（ <a href="/artists/Roisin-Murphy">Roisin Murphy</a> ）等人演奏了这首歌。</p><p> 《潜水者》以梦幻般的吉他和贝斯连复段开场，摩尔唱道： <em>“他们发现了你的水彩画和未用完的燃料”。</em>在一份声明中谈到这首歌时，摩尔分享道：“《潜水员》以一位潜水员在创作这些歌曲时在日内瓦湖水下迷失的真实故事作为专辑的结尾。 </p><p><iframe title="潜水员" width="696" height="522" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/CXNiMh1-PsQ?feature=oembed&enablejsapi=1" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p> “潜水员正在探索深海，研究一个不受人类破坏的世界，但几天后才被发现，他的生命已经屈服于野外。这首歌是整张专辑的结尾，一首重复的钢琴曲，就像呼叫、铃声、警报般的旋律。”</p><p>这首歌是继之前发行的《Isadora》、《Hypnogram》、《Rewilding》和《Sans Limites》之后，其中由<a href="/artists/Stereolab">Stereolab</a>的 Lætitia Sadier 演唱的歌曲。所有单曲都将收录在<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/sonic-youth">Sonic Youth</a>联合创始人的专辑《 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/thurston-moore-announces-new-album-flow-critical-lucidity-3767469">Flow Critical Lucidity</a> 》中，该专辑将于 9 月 20 日通过 Daydream Library Series 发行。您可以<a href="https://lnk.to/FlowCriticalLucidity" target="_blank" rel="noopener">在此处预订/预先保存</a>。</p><p><strong>瑟斯顿摩尔“Flow Critical Lucidity”曲目列表是：</strong></p><p> <strong>1.“新城”</strong><br /> <strong>2.“无限制”</strong><br /> <strong>3.“影子”</strong><br /> <strong>4.《催眠图》</strong><br /> <strong>5.《我们嗨起来》</strong><br /> <strong>6.“野化”</strong><br /> <strong>7.《潜水员》</strong><br /> <strong>&#39;Isadora (Bedazzled Mix)&#39; – （附赠曲目包含在透明软盘上</strong>） </p><p></p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/C_DkP13sLAd/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></div></div><div style="padding: 19% 0;"></div><div style="display:block; height:50px; margin:0 auto 12px; width:50px;"><svg width="50px" height="50px" viewBox="0 0 60 60" version="1.1" xmlns="https://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="https://www.w3.org/1999/xlink"><g stroke="none" stroke-width="1" fill="none" fill-rule="evenodd"><g transform="translate(-511.000000, -20.000000)" fill="#000000"><g><path d="M556.869,30.41 C554.814,30.41 553.148,32.076 553.148,34.131 C553.148,36.186 554.814,37.852 556.869,37.852 C558.924,37.852 560.59,36.186 560.59,34.131 C560.59,32.076 558.924,30.41 556.869,30.41 M541,60.657 C535.114,60.657 530.342,55.887 530.342,50 C530.342,44.114 535.114,39.342 541,39.342 C546.887,39.342 551.658,44.114 551.658,50 C551.658,55.887 546.887,60.657 541,60.657 M541,33.886 C532.1,33.886 524.886,41.1 524.886,50 C524.